headline: Target Announces Limited-time Collection with Woolrich, Blending Iconic Heritage and Trend-forward Style
summary: Target Corporation (NYSE: TGT) today announced the launch of a limited-time collection with Woolrich, the iconic outdoor lifestyle brand known for its signature buffalo check. Woolrich x Target launches Oct. 18 in select Target stores and on Target.com, featuring more than 100 reinvented classics that blend Woolrich's heritage of outdoor craftsmanship with modern style across men's and women's apparel, home, outdoor gear and food and beverage.
